@startuml
'https://plantuml.com/sequence-diagram

skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor black
    ActorBorderColor BACBFC
    ActorBackgroundColor BACBFC
    LifeLineBorderColor blue
    LifeLineBackgroundColor lightblue

    ParticipantBorderColor D6E0FD
    ParticipantBackgroundColor D6E0FD
}
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor SmokeWhite

autonumber

actor User
participant "Frontend\n(Browser)" as Frontend
participant "NextJs Backend\n(NextAuth)" as Backend
participant "Customer service" as Customer
participant "Okta AuthorizationServer\n(default)" as Okta

=== Logout flow ==

User -> Frontend: User clicks logout button
activate Frontend
Frontend -> Backend: callGlobalSignOut(callbackUrl)
activate Backend
Backend -> Customer: clearSessionsAndTokens()
activate Customer
Customer -> Okta: DELETE /api/v1/users/{userId}/sessions
activate Okta
Backend -> Frontend: await response
deactivate Customer
deactivate Okta
Frontend -> Backend: call signOut()
Backend -> Frontend: return and delete session cookie
Frontend -> Backend: Follow callbackUrl (usually landing page)
Backend -> Frontend: Render /auth/signout-landing

deactivate Backend
Frontend -> Frontend: optional other activity (e.g. redirect to CMS landing page)
@enduml
